Description: 
  The *hssGWAS* package is designed to facilitate the standardisation of GWAS 
  summary statistics. It reformats inputted summary statisitics to include 
  SNP, CHR, BP and can look up these values if any are missing. It also removes 
  duplicates across SNPs.
URL: https://github.com/neurogenomics/hssGWAS
